🏠 ADMIN DASHBOARD — OVERVIEW SECTION
Operational + Maturity Snapshot Layer

0️⃣ CORE DESIGN RULE
Overview answers:
    1. What is happening right now?
    2. Are we stable?
    3. Is execution healthy?
    4. Do we need intervention?
    5. Where are we in maturity (L0 → L3)?

Data Sources (Strict)
Allowed:
students (HOT aggregate fields only)
runAnalytics (current academic year)
studentYearMetrics (aggregated)
governanceSnapshots (L3 only)
license document
Not allowed:
sessions
rawAttempts
per-question logs
Everything must be precomputed.

1️⃣ LAYOUT STRUCTURE
Overview
   ├── Operational Snapshot
   ├── Current Activity
   ├── Performance Summary (30-day)
   ├── Execution Summary (L1+)
   ├── Risk Snapshot (L2+)
   ├── Governance Snapshot (L3)
   ├── System Health & Licensing
Responsive grid.
Max 8–12 cards visible at once.

