4️⃣ PERFORMANCE SUMMARY (LAST 30 DAYS)
Replace “Score” everywhere with:
    • Avg % Raw Marks
    • Avg % Accuracy
Never show legacy score.

🟢 L0
Show:
    • Avg % Raw (30 days)
    • Avg % Accuracy (30 days)
    • Highest Performing Batch
    • Lowest Performing Batch
    • Participation Rate
    • Distribution Chart (simple histogram)
No behavioral metrics.

🟡 L1 Adds
Behavior overlays:
    • Avg Phase Adherence %
    • Easy Neglect %
    • Hard Bias %
    • Time Misallocation %
Now performance becomes interpretive.

🔵 L2 Adds
Structural compliance:
    • Risk Distribution
    • Avg Discipline Index
    • Controlled Mode Improvement Delta
    • Execution Stability Badge
Badge Logic:
Stable ≥ 75
Moderate 60–75
High Variance < 60

